data.description: Welcome to 3422 Plumstead Avenue.     This is an affordable beautifully classic twin home in Drexel Hill on a nice, quiet street is  Move-in ready at a great new price!!! Enter into the sunny enclosed front porch which leads to the spacious first-floor living room with a gas fireplace. This home features a large formal dining room, an updated kitchen with granite countertops, a new bathroom, and a walk-out basement. Large walk-up third-floor attic space could be a great 4th bedroom, walkup closet, or an office.  Shared driveway with a nice big backyard to use for entertaining, relaxing, or adding a garage.   The whole house has been freshly painted and the original hardwood floors with beautiful walnut inlay have just been refinished. Windows have been recently replaced throughout and come with a lifetime warranty.   This rare find is move-in ready and waiting for you to call it home.
